    <!--
    INSTRUCTIONS FOR UPDATING:

    1. After building a new version, create a .zip of the app:
       cd makeHTML-Swift/build
       zip -r makeHTML-VERSION.zip makeHTML.app

    2. Create a GitHub release and upload the .zip file

    3. Generate the EdDSA signature (see SETUP.md for key generation):
       ./sign_update.sh makeHTML-VERSION.zip

    4. Get the file size:
       ls -l makeHTML-VERSION.zip

    5. Add a new <item> below with the details

    6. Commit and push this file to GitHub
    -->

